{"word":"ναυβάτης","slug":"ναυβάτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ναυβάτης</b></el> <el>(νᾰυ-βάτης, ου, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βαίνω'><el>βαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a \"ship-goer,\" a seaman</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a>, <el>ν. στρατός</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; <el>στόλος</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}